                "This proposal would have made a minor technical revision to the entry for H-30(C) in the table of contents at the beginning of this appendix and republishes sample form H-30(C). The technical change amends \u201cSample Form of Periodic Statement for a Payment-Options Loan (\u00a7\u20091026.41)\u201d to \u201cSample Form of Periodic Statement for a Payment-Option Loan (\u00a7\u20091026.41).\u201d The Bureau is adopting this technical change as proposed."
