                "The 2013 TILA Servicing Final Rule changed the commentary to \u00a7\u20091026.19(b) to reflect the revised \u00a7\u20091026.20(c) and revised \u00a7\u20091026.20(d) ARM notices. This proposal would have modified the Variable-Rate Mortgage Sample form in appendix H-14 to reflect the language in the revised commentary. The Bureau is adopting these modifications as proposed. No change to the table of contents of appendix H is necessary."
